ggests that more\ncoesite-like and quartz-like local structures emerge in silica glasses when the\ndensity is at a minimum during the heating process.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 14 Nov 2021 21:20:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 23 Aug 2022 22:30:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-25"}
