we provide an analytical method for computing\nequilibria in networks with only two nodes, and show that it is possible for a\nbivirus network to have an unstable coexistence equilibrium and two locally\nstable boundary equilibria.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Nov 2021 02:57:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-16"}
