emental D/H in the molecular envelopes and hot corino\nare derived. In addition, B5 IRS1, L1455-IRS1 and L1551-IRS5 show a low\nexcitation methanol line, suggesting an origin from an extended structure,\nplausibly UV illuminated. The abundance ratios of iCOMs with respect CH3OH\nmeasured towards the L1551-IRS5 hot corino and the deuteration in our sample\nare comparable to that estimated at earlier stages, as well as to that found in\ncomets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Nov 2021 07:42:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-14"}
